high_descs: walk over to the kitchen sink on the left side of the room
grab the butter knife off of the back side of the left side kitchen sink
turn right and walk over to the kitchen table in the corner of the room on the way right
slice up the tomato there on the table into slices
turn around and walk back over to the kitchen sink
place the butter knife down in the kitchen sink on the right
turn right and walk back over to the kitchen table in the right corner of the room
grab an tomato slice off of the kitchen table
turn around and walk back over to the sink
put the tomato slice in the kitchen sink on the right, rinse if off, and then take it back out
turn right and walk to the counter, turn right and walk to the fridge, turn left and walk to the wall at the end of the room, turn right and walk to the table, finally turn right to face table
place the tomato slice down on the table in between the two tomatoes there

high_descs: Walk towards the refrigerator, turn left, walk towards the sink.
Pick up the knife that is on the left side of the sink, sitting on a tray.

Take the knife and turn right then walk towards the counter, then turn right again and walk towards garbage can hang a left then walk towards the window, turn right again and walk towards the brown table.
Take the knife and slice the tomato on the table.
Take the knife, turn around and walk towards the counter top. Turn left and walk towards the refrigerator, turn right and walk towards the sink.
Place the knife next to the glass in the sink.
Turn right and walk towards the counter, turn right again and walk towards the garbage can, the turn left and walk towards the window, hang a right and walk towards the brown table.
Pick up a tomato slice from the table.
Turn around and walk towards the counter top, then turn left and walk towards the refrigerator, hang a right and walk towards the sink.
Place the tomato slice next to the knife in the sink and turn the water on to rinse the tomato slice, then turn the water off and pick up the slice of tomato in the sink.

Turn right and walk towards the the counter, turn right and walk towards the garbage can, turn left and walk all the way towards the window, then turn right and walk towards the brown chair closest to the wall.
Place the tomato slice in between two tomatoes.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of tomato in between two tomatoes on the table closest to the wall.

Pick up the knife on the metal plate to the left of the sink.
Turn right, head towards the counter, turn right towards the end of the counter, turn left and then hang right towards the circle table.
Cut the tomato on the table into several slices.
Turn around, head towards the counter, make a slight left and hang right towards the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn right, head towards the counter, turn right towards the end of the counter, turn left and then hang right towards the circle table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn around, head towards the counter, make a slight left and hang right towards the sink.
Place the tomato in the sink wash it and pick it back up.
Turn right, head towards the counter, turn right towards the end of the counter, turn left and then hang right towards the circle table.
Place the tomato in between the other two tomatoes on the table.

Pink up the knife on the left side of the sink
Turn to your right move a little the turn right head to the round table
Slice the tomato into pieces on the table
Turn around to your right, walk straight then left then head to the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Turn to your right,move a forward then head to the round table
Pick a slice of tomato

Put the tomato in the sink and rinse it
